collectible.name: Web3vm Light Blue Logo Mask
collectible.description: This token was designed by Scott H. Stevenson for the Regency project in CryptoVoxels. It is intended as a wearable and used as a token to unlock content in Swag0x, Web3vm, CityWide, Bluefin, Airdrop, Underjaw and Worldlaw parcels. It also attaches to additional out-of-game content.
